We are still preparing a lot to do these things, and we will be able to create synergy with RENC crypto currency.

Title: âœ…[ANN][PRE-SALE] ğŸš€ RENC - P2P Car sharing PLATFORM ğŸš€âœ…
Body: RENC was born for the new concept of P2P Car sharing service.  When we move forward anywhere, everyone will use car sharing, by providing a car owned by an individual to Car Sharing and allowing others to use it, the car provider will be able to get the sharing fee And the user will conveniently use the Sharing Car.  In addition, existing rental companies register their cars on our the RENC Sharing Platform and participate in the sharing service with other cars they will be able to generate revenue.  The RENC platform also allows users who do not have a Driver License to search for nearby drivers, you can move it. After all,  drivers who do not have a car can make money by this model.  So, RENC is a model that can be participated by any vehicle provider, vehicle user or driver.  As a payment method, RENC crypto-currency will be used in combination with credit card usage. After use, 2% cash back you will be returned to the RENC coin. It is a service that rewards you when you write a review or give experience to our community. RENC is a car sharing platform and blockchain that does not mining like any other coin, but uses a Sharing car and rewards everyone who participates in the community.
